com.strandgenomics.imaging.iclient
Class RecordBuilder

java.lang.Object
  com.strandgenomics.imaging.iclient.ImageSpaceObject
      com.strandgenomics.imaging.iclient.RecordBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Disposable, Serializable
public class RecordBuilder
extends ImageSpaceObject

RecordBuilder is notional record under construction. Record can be built by providing initial record metadata and adding image data one by one.

Author:
Anup Kulkarni
See Also:

channels - channels
sites - sites
imageWidth - width of every image in record under construction
imageHeight - height of every image in record under construction
pixelDepth - depth of pixel
pixelSizeX - x-size (in micron) of the pixel
pixelSizeY - y-size (in micron) of the pixel
pixelSizeZ - z-size (in micron) of the pixel
imageType - type of the image, by default it is Gray-scale
sourceFormat - file format of the original source files
